{"tid":794601,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[工程撚][物管撚] 屋企出現裂縫點算？","createTime":"2018-08-26T11:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T09:22:28.000Z","uid":144567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"81e208c0f74c6f8e46ed5b4b048161ffd9f4c377","tid":794601,"uid":144567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"位置係屋企入面 大門頂部<br />\n我發現屋企度大門閂唔埋 <br />\n情況就係度門右邊向下傾斜 門角直接打落門框度<br />\n要向上頂一頂先閂到門<br />\n之後就發現門頂有一大條裂縫<br />\n<br />\n我想問喱類大廈結構問題搵管理處適唔適當？<br />\n如果要自費維修 成隻門換幾錢左右？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/191524_5f6688fcfb0f99560253d6257399912c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F191524_5f6688fcfb0f99560253d6257399912c.png&h=1633e2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/191526_08f740224c5d48517b350f8531e0c348.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F191526_08f740224c5d48517b350f8531e0c348.png&h=d9355cfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40788acc1a271771798db7e2fd95eb49871b63ea","tid":794601,"uid":119769,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0db7acceab6242959d26398bd6b23e1bd9b94670","tid":794601,"uid":2277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"自己上翻灰啦 唔同爛石矢咩"},{"pid":"e08b0c9e8979e70cb7a4835c1e89d15cec614686","tid":794601,"uid":121911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"無事 門上面通常係吊扇定住門框 明顯係個吊扇無鐵開始裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以你點極最終都會裂 除非拆左個門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96963dd866732bd3bfa84f0aeae840ae03f7b250","tid":794601,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"係。。咁先。。。啦"},{"pid":"c668f34c0fe102b1315c0eb9229ad760dde55b70","tid":794601,"uid":72477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"我做咁多年物管既經驗話我知<br />\n似係你道門框變形/ 門鉸位鬆左<br />\n門框離磚有裂縫<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔關大廈結構事<br />\n而係屋入面管理處多數叫你閣下自理<br />\n<br />\n屋企道大門係唔係長期開住？"},{"pid":"e80fc5e0ec4ef4ed3b0f6f1fe2d340e6b6da1ad5","tid":794601,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"係咪地鐵沿線?"},{"pid":"9e37aa726813655308e8dcc95c74aa35b1c03d02","tid":794601,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"可能係個底框鬆咗<br />\n如果對道門影響唔大就搵啲油漆灰遮住條gap<br />\n影響大就搵裝置佬拆門，連埋底框拆"},{"pid":"3d098246b62a56c56053298ce13ec6dd64ec72e1","tid":794601,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c668f34c0fe102b1315c0eb9229ad760dde55b70","tid":794601,"uid":72477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"我做咁多年物管既經驗話我知<br />\n似係你道門框變形/ 門鉸位鬆左<br />\n門框離磚有裂縫<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔關大廈結構事<br />\n而係屋入面管理處多數叫你閣下自理<br />\n<br />\n屋企道大門係唔係長期開住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"正路門頂上面有條黏土，唔會直接係磚"},{"pid":"1a8d759d91f1c91d47f54982ca47c889bb582564","tid":794601,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"修口野 你用多十年廿年都唔會有事"},{"pid":"14267cfb388977e9a98d3a99252112d200f46bf0","tid":794601,"uid":142903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"門框老化冷縮熱脹<br />\n<br />\n利申驗樓師"},{"pid":"150e96316d8ad93ee4049182b96fd61063dd8325","tid":794601,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"認真, 先將條隙用剷刀剷大條d, 再用玻璃膠填條隙, 批灰批平佢, 再油就搞掂晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab859f95b51675f9f98d5af408c750f80155d635","tid":794601,"uid":132338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"150e96316d8ad93ee4049182b96fd61063dd8325","tid":79